@Borthwick @AliceAlbrecht @gordonbrander @Mappletons

@PNCBank_Help I didn't answer satisfaction survey because: 

Your rep was perfect, but your platform sucks. My January 2022 trouble ticket is still not fixed, but your rep sorted me out and we solved my problem. 

