@farnamstreet yesterday you cited Howard Bloom with this great quote, but I think it's @JamesGleick: 

It is not the amount of knowledge that makes a brain. It is not even the distribution of knowledge. It is the interconnectedness.

Some connections here: https://t.co/QHL4a5fdXv

